{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/markdowns/react/atomic_design/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Maeng's Blog","author":"Maeng","comment":{"utterances":"maeng2418/maeng2418.github.io"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3eab5564-51e9-5be2-be56-fe2dedf5a966","excerpt":"…","html":"<h2 id=\"아토믹-디자인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%84%ED%86%A0%EB%AF%B9-%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"아토믹 디자인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>아토믹 디자인</h2>\n<p>디자인 요소들을 나누어 파악하고 이 요소들을 조합을 통해서 디자인을 구성하는 방식. 즉, 컴포넌트 중심의 디자인 패턴.</p>\n<p>리액트는 컴포넌트를 중심으로 만들어지는 프레임워크로, 컴포넌트의 재사용성이 매우 중요하다. 중복이 되는 컴포넌트를 공통으로 사용할 수 있도록 빼는 것이 관건인데, 이것은 개발을 진행하다 보면 일일히 생각하며 진행하는 것이 어렵다. 결국에는 중복되는 코드가 많아지고, 이를 관리하는 것이 어려워지게 되는 것이다. 그렇기에 개발 단계 처음부터 재사용성이 용이하며, 여러 개의 컴포넌트들을 모아 또 다른 컴포넌트를 만들 수 있도록(조립) 고민하며 개발하는 것이 아토믹 디자인이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"컴포넌트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"컴포넌트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>컴포넌트</h2>\n<p>하나의 컴포넌트는 한 가지 일을 하는게 이상적(단일 책임 원칙)</p>\n<h2 id=\"컴포넌트-분리-기준\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8-%EB%B6%84%EB%A6%AC-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80\" aria-label=\"컴포넌트 분리 기준 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>컴포넌트 분리 기준</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"atomic design 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/97d8c798f6f2716d66fc26dec55ab5b7/1cfc2/atomic_design_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/97d8c798f6f2716d66fc26dec55ab5b7/3684f/atomic_design_1.png 225w,\n/static/97d8c798f6f2716d66fc26dec55ab5b7/fc2a6/atomic_design_1.png 450w,\n/static/97d8c798f6f2716d66fc26dec55ab5b7/1cfc2/atomic_design_1.png 900w,\n/static/97d8c798f6f2716d66fc26dec55ab5b7/c1b63/atomic_design_1.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><img src=\"/1ba101c4e022c660ed66c0340e14735c/atomic_design_2.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"아톰-atoms\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%84%ED%86%B0-atoms\" aria-label=\"아톰 atoms permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>아톰 (Atoms)</h2>\n<p>Label, Input, CheckBox, Select같은 HTML 태그 같이 기능적/의미론적으로 가장 작은 단위의 컴포넌트.</p>\n<p>특정 기능을 수행하는 것이 아니라 일반적으로 사용할 수 있도록 구현.</p>\n<p>ex) Input 태그의 onChange와 값이 어딘가에 종속되지 않도록 props로 전달받아 사용.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 642px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.44444444444445%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAYAAADDl76dAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAhUlEQVR42q2QyQoDIRBE/f9f9OweyUEF90rawDCZyXZIwUO7qS5aGX7QnHNxrF/BUkrgnOPqLg8z5imwtYYQAmKMG6UU9N6fIB+j1For+r14pzHGaZig/hGGP2sLpCcQOee1Ma1P5763/8ePgWRUSkEIAefcunvvIaWEtRbGGGitV+i3wBsh99kAt5cdXgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"atomic design 3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8f7a5ab03825d80f1c577a1ce102f6e6/1bba8/atomic_design_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f7a5ab03825d80f1c577a1ce102f6e6/3684f/atomic_design_3.png 225w,\n/static/8f7a5ab03825d80f1c577a1ce102f6e6/fc2a6/atomic_design_3.png 450w,\n/static/8f7a5ab03825d80f1c577a1ce102f6e6/1bba8/atomic_design_3.png 642w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"모큘-molecules\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A8%ED%81%98-molecules\" aria-label=\"모큘 molecules permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>모큘 (Molecules)</h2>\n<p>Atoms를 조합한 컴포넌트. Label + (Input | CheckBox | Select) 조합으로 FormItem 이라는 컴포넌트를 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"atomic design 4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c00567decf4bfbd713ce082dfcee266a/e85cb/atomic_design_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c00567decf4bfbd713ce082dfcee266a/3684f/atomic_design_4.png 225w,\n/static/c00567decf4bfbd713ce082dfcee266a/fc2a6/atomic_design_4.png 450w,\n/static/c00567decf4bfbd713ce082dfcee266a/e85cb/atomic_design_4.png 480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"올가니즘-organisms\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%AC%EA%B0%80%EB%8B%88%EC%A6%98-organisms\" aria-label=\"올가니즘 organisms permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>올가니즘 (Organisms)</h2>\n<p>Molecule과 Atoms를 조합. FormItem 여러 개와 버튼을 조합하여 SignUpForm을 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<p>Organism 역시 특정 기능을 직접적으로 수행하진 않지만, 특정한 컴포넌트들을 조합하다 보니 재사용성이 조금 떨어짐</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 410px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 105.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"atomic design 5\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3e9fd4d220f36c93222c9e05fcf7f0c3/d68e4/atomic_design_5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3e9fd4d220f36c93222c9e05fcf7f0c3/3684f/atomic_design_5.png 225w,\n/static/3e9fd4d220f36c93222c9e05fcf7f0c3/d68e4/atomic_design_5.png 410w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"템플릿-templates\" style